name: Aarsix
content:
Aarsix was a male humanoid who served the Galactic Republic during the Galactic War against the Sith Empire. In 3642 BBY, he was stationed in the Republic Operational Headquarters on the planet Quesh during the Republicâ€“Empire conflict there. He worked selling heavy armor from a stall.
Aarsix wore yellow-colored full body armor while at his stall, which was exposed to Quesh's toxic atmosphere. He also carried a blaster rifle.
Aarsix first appeared in the 2011 massively multiplayer online role playing game Star Wars: The Old Republic, which was created by BioWare. In the game, he served as a heavy armor vendor on Quesh. His location is also marked on a map of Quesh in 2011 Prima Games' Star Wars: The Old Republic Explorer's Guide, although the guide refers to him as "Aarssix."
